  "prompt": "What are sticker packs in criminal case and how are they useful in the game?",
  "response": "Sticker packs in \"Criminal Case\" are collections of stickers that players can obtain and use within the game. These stickers can be earned through various means such as progressing through levels, completing certain tasks, or purchasing them. Here's how they are useful:\n\n1. **Reward System:** Sticker packs often serve as rewards for completing cases, achievements, or daily challenges. They provide an incentive for players to engage more deeply with the game.\n\n2. **Social Interaction:** Players can use stickers to communicate with friends and other players within the game. It's a fun way to express emotions, reactions, or messages.\n\n3. **Game Progression:** Some stickers might be part of collections that, when completed, can grant players special bonuses, items, or additional energy. This adds an element of collecting and completionism to the game.\n\n4. **Customization:** Stickers allow players to personalize their gaming experience. Whether it's customizing a chat or profile, stickers add a fun and unique touch.\n\nOverall, sticker packs add a layer of engagement and interactivity to \"Criminal Case,\" making the game more enjoyable and rewarding for players.",
